headline: Allstate Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates on Property-Liability Unit Strength
summary: ALL's Q4 earnings beat estimates. Property-Liability strength, lower catastrophe losses and higher earned premiums drive an 86.6% year-over-year EPS surge.
